						               													<description>You are an ambitious magistrate with a decree from the king to build the best hamlet possible. But building a hamlet isn't just about a robust economy and zoning laws. You have to negotiate the political landscape, deal with crazy things like dwarven larceny and ogre attacks, and build a wildly successful military while also bringing culture to your uncouth citizens.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Super Hardcore Hamlet Builder Pro 5000 Of The Stars; 1599 AD (or just Hamlet Builder Pro for short), each player will design and build their own hamlets. You can start off small with tents and mining camps, and work your way up to smelters, blacksmiths, siege factories and more. But you can't just focus on military, after all, your people need to eat. Many will want a better place to sleep, too, and that is just the beginning of your job as magistrate.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Over 7 rounds of game play, each player will build a couple dozen buildings into their hamlet, while managing their income, storage, military, and culture. Each round presents a new challenge. Will you be a Hamlet Builder Pro?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
